quran[11{c,v,t}:
33,63,log tum se qayamat ki nisbat daryaft karte hain ( ke kab aeye gi ) keh do ke is ka ilm khuda hi ko hai. aur tumhekiya maloom hai shayad qayamat qareeb hi aagai ho
33,64,be shak khuda ne kafiroon par laanat ki hai aur un ke liye ( jahannum ki ) aag tayyar kar rakhi hai
33,65,is meinabdul aabaad rahen ge. nah kisi ko dost payen ge aur nah madadgaar
33,66,jis din un ke munh aag mein ultaye jayen ge kahin ae kash hum khuda ki farmabardari karte aur rasool ( khuda ) ka hukum mantay
33,67,aur kahin ge ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar hum ne apne sardaro aur barray logon ka kaha maana to unhon ne hum ko raste se gumraah kardiya
33,68,ae hamaray perwar-digaar un ko dugna azaab day aur un par barri laanat kar
33,69,momino tum un logon jaisay nah hona jinhon ne moose ( ko aib laga kar ) ranj pohanchaya to khuda ne un ko be aib saabitkiya. aur woh khuda ke nazdeek aabaroo walay they
33,70,momino khuda se dara karo aur baat seedhi kaha karo
33,71,woh tumahray aamaal durust kardey ga aur tumahray gunah bakhash day ga. aur jo shakhs khuda aur is ke rasool ki farmabardari kere ga to be shak barri morad paye ga
33,72,hum ne ( baar ) amanat ko asmano aur zameen par paishkiya to unhon ne is ke uthany se inkaarkiya aur is se dar gay. aur ensaan ne is ko utha liya. be shak woh zalim aur jaahil tha
33,73,taakay khuda munhafiq mardon aur munhafiq aurton aur mushriq mardon aur mushriq aurton ko azaab day aur khuda momin mardon aur momin aurton par meharbani kere. aur khuda to bakhsnay wala meharban hai
